column4: Cisco profit edges past estimates despite weak telecom spending
column5: Cisco Systems Inc's  quarterly profit edged past market estimates as demand for new switches  routers  wireless gear and servers made up for sluggish spending by telecom customers and weak sales in emerging markets.
